data.Name: Beak Nasty
data.Bio: Producer/DJ Beak Nasty (a.k.a. Beaker), has been surrounded by music his entire life. His music can be described as a hybrid of electronic music and instrumental hip hop. Within a year of releasing his first track, he has opened for acts such as DJ Abilities, Dead Prez, MartyParty, and Toki Wright, and all signs are pointing towards bigger things to come. Enjoy the ride. Read more on Last.fm
